## M22: raw `%x` access outside a `raw` block is rejected.
##
## Per GPT-5.5 entries 35 + 38: raw access is the archetypal
## unsafe operation. Without an enclosing `raw` block, the
## operation is sema-rejected with a tailored diagnostic
## pointing the user at the fix.

sub main()
  x = 7
  r = %x           # error: raw access outside `raw` block
